title: Ellough industrial estate workshop fire tackled by crews
title_page: Ellough industrial estate workshop fire tackled by crews - BBC News
maintext:
Firefighters have extinguished a blaze at a workshop on an industrial estate.
Crews from Suffolk Fire and Rescue Service were called to Benacre Road near Ellough just after 07:00 GMT.
A spokesperson said the blaze was within a single storey workshop that was 60m (197ft) by 20m (66ft).
Residents nearby were warned to keep all windows and doors closed before firefighters had the blaze under control by 10:15.
